{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "editable": false,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "datasource": null,
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Compliance evidence (CS22 — SOX / PCI-DSS / GDPR)\n\nThis dashboard visualizes the compliance-relevant signals the running system already emits so an auditor or operator can watch **segregation-of-duties (SoD) enforcement**, **access-governance activity** (grants issued/revoked, recertification runs), and **authorization outcomes** (permit/deny ratios across the PDP, entitlements, and edge gateway) over time.\n\nIt is operational evidence that the access controls are actually enforced at runtime, and it complements the static control-to-signal mapping in `docs/compliance/control-mapping.md`."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "SoD denials over time (governance.access.request → Deny)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 15, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 1 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "sum(rate(pdp_decisions_total{action=\"governance.access.request\",decision=\"Deny\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "SoD denials/s", "range": true } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "SoD denials by reason code",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 1 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "sum by (reason) (rate(pdp_decisions_total{action=\"governance.access.request\",decision=\"Deny\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{reason}}", "range": true } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Governance decisions by outcome",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 1 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "sum by (outcome) (rate(governance_decisions_total[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{outcome}}", "range": true } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Access grants issued vs revoked",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 1 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "sum(rate(governance_grants_issued_total[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "grants issued/s", "range": true },
        { "refId": "B", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" }, "editorMode": "code", "expr": "sum(rate(governance_grants_revoked_total[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "grants revoked/s", "range": true }
      ]
    },
    {
